<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div xml:id="PN219-intro">
      <p type="edition">tiṇaiyum tuṟaiyum avai. avaṉ vaṭakkiruntāṉaik karuvūrp peruñcattukattuppūttaṉār pāṭiyatu.
      </p>
      <p xml:lang="en" type="translation">  
      </p>
    </div>
    <div xml:id="PN219">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>uḷḷāṟṟuk kavalaip puḷḷi nīḻaṉ</l>
<l>muḻūu vaḷḷūra muṇakku maḷḷa</l>
<l>pulavuti mātō nīyē</l>
<l>palarā lattainiṉ kuṟiyirun tōrē.</l>
</lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>O warrior whose whole meat is drying up</l>
<l>in the dappled shade on the crossroad of the inner path,</l>
<l>would you be vexed [now]?</l>
<l>Many indeed are those who sit at your sign.</l>
</lg>
    </div>
